title: jennybrow
author: jennybrow
content: Hello everybody,we process payments and funds for different B2B clients around the world.We need people able to manage multiple Stripe accounts on a regular basis.We are professional and serious, and we handle large sums of money.Pay is very HIGH, up to 15% on each transaction.You must:1. be reliable, punctual (7 days), responsible;2. know how to handle Stripe accounts (if you are very skilled in Paypal, in some cases Paypal accounts can do the job), get verified, and have a bank account linked for every account.PM me if interested.
